---
title: Sweet Potato & Quinoa Bowl with Avocado, Almonds & Feta
description: Three super foods in one bowl? Believe it! We've packed major power into this nutrient-rice dish. Quinoa, avocado, and sweet potatoes are some of the most delicious ingredients out there and they happen to be some of the healthiest to boot! Peppery arugula, tangy orange, and crunchy almonds add the perfect mix of flavor and texture.
